# ============================================================
# CSED332 Project .gitignore
# Purpose: Prevent binary/intermediate files from being committed
# ============================================================
#
# ⚠️ TA WARNING (Effective from Assignment 3):
# 1. Do NOT include binary or intermediate files (.class, .jar)
# 2. Run "sbt clean" before making a commit
# 3. Review staged changes carefully (git diff --staged)
# 4. Do NOT use "git add -A" or "git add ."
# 5. Errors from unwanted files will affect your grade!
#
# Reference: TA Notice from Seonggon Namgung
# ============================================================

# ============================================================
